1. *Pitaj* me zašto sam se tako ponašao. (Ask me why I behaved like that.)
2. Samo *pitaj* oca. (Just ask your father.)
3. On je zaista *pitao* pitanja. (He was really asking questions.)
4. Ona je *pitala* zašto nismo otišli. (She asked why we didn't go.)
5. *Pitanje* je ostalo bez odgovora. (The question remained unanswered.)
6. On je *pitanjima* uvek tragao za odgovorima. (He was always searching for answers with questions.)